                            Label: "bow_out_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are bound for Scorchspire and Vulcan - the last badge before the League. Warm up on my fire first, or decline and save it for the summit. Your call."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The ground here is warm even in winter and the air tastes of struck matches. A Cinderfall bout now beats meeting Vulcan cold - but walking on is free enough."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Vulcan and the last gym sit up the skirt of the volcano. Take a bout to test your team against real Fire, or step past me. No shame in declining on the last approach."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Default",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
